{"name":"UnicodeBasic","instances":[],"imports":["Init","UnicodeBasic.Types","UnicodeBasic.UnicodeData","UnicodeBasic.PropList"],"declarations":[{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L863-L864","name":"Unicode.isAlphanum","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isAlphanum","doc":"Check if alphabetic or digit character\n\nUnicode properties: `Alphabetic`, `Numeric_Type=Digit` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L858-L858","name":"Unicode.isAlpha","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isAlpha","doc":"Check if alphabetic character\n\nUnicode property: `Alphabetic` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L849-L855","name":"Unicode.isAlphabetic","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isAlphabetic","doc":"Check if alphabetic character\n\nUnicode property: `Alphabetic` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L843-L844","name":"Unicode.isMath","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isMath","doc":"Check if mathematical symbol character\n\nUnicode property: `Math` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L812-L838","name":"Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","kind":"def","docLink":"./UnicodeBasic.html#Unicode.isCaseIgnorable","doc":"Check if character is ignorable for casing purposes\n\nGenerated from general categories `Lm`, `Mn`, `Me`, `Sk`, `Cf`, and word\nbreak properties `MidLetter`, `MidNumLet`, `Single_Quote`.\n\nUnicode property: `Case_Ignorable` "},{"sourceLink":"https://github.com/fgdorais/lean4-unicode-basic/blob/c7360dcdfc4ef13e1accbe83280656d8348839fa/UnicodeBasic.lean#L798-L804"